    "description": "由于迫降，炸药已在多个城市种植，使整个城市处于危险之中。<br>在这种危机情况下，作为一名特工，你的任务是阻止这颗定时炸弹，同时保护它不被引爆。<br><br>滴答作响的定时炸弹只有1分钟！<br>为了确保城市居民在危险中的安全，你建立了一个专门的防御系统，可以增加滴答作响的定时炸弹的持续时间。<br>每个城市都有特殊的装备和队伍，你要争取时间，克服各种障碍和威胁，将炸弹化解到底。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/fca50fcf3e0457ed3a08f83498f6d6fb.poster.avif?t=1679994677\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/fca50fcf3e0457ed3a08f83498f6d6fb.webm?t=1679994677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/fca50fcf3e0457ed3a08f83498f6d6fb.mp4?t=1679994677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>但是腾出时间绝非易事。在这个游戏中有各种各样的障碍阻碍你。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/d367ab1c9354d68b7631cbb503482e74.poster.avif?t=1679994677\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/d367ab1c9354d68b7631cbb503482e74.webm?t=1679994677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/d367ab1c9354d68b7631cbb503482e74.mp4?t=1679994677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/34b49732008ee4f819de583bb344b753.poster.avif?t=1679994677\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/34b49732008ee4f819de583bb344b753.webm?t=1679994677\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337500/extras/34b49732008ee4f819de583bb344b753.mp4?t=1679994677\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>各种障碍，例如控制你的视力或阻碍你的听力，将阻止你为滴答作响的定时炸弹争取时间。<br><br>那你现在应该怎么办？您必须以出色的身体和策略来克服这场危机。在这个城市，你必须尽最大努力保护炸药桶中的定时炸弹。<br>你是改变这座城市命运的最后希望。你能放慢滴答作响的定时炸弹的速度并停止计时吗？",
